Human Capital Management
Chevron invests in its employees and culture, with the objective of developing the full potential of its workforce to deliver energy
solutions and drive human progress. The Chevron Way explains the company’s beliefs, vision, purpose and values. It guides how
the company’s employees work and establishes a common understanding of culture and aspirations. Chevron hires, develops, and
strives to retain a diverse workforce of high-performing talent, and fosters a culture that values diversity, inclusion and employee
engagement. Chevron leadership is accountable for the company’s investment in people and the company’s culture. This includes
reviews of metrics addressing critical function hiring, leadership development, retention, diversity and inclusion, and employee
engagement.
